</span></span></span></code></pre></div><p>也就是 480分钟（8个小时），北京时间是东八区，刚好与格林威治时间相差8个小时，这说明 <code>getTimezoneOffset()</code> 方法是很有效的。</p>
<p>接下来利用这个方法，判断一下当前时区是否为夏令时。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-js" data-lang="js"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">const</span> time1 = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> <span style="color:#658b00">Date</span>(<span style="color:#b452cd">2021</span>, <span style="color:#b452cd">0</span>, <span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">const</span> time2 = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> <span style="color:#658b00">Date</span>(<span style="color:#b452cd">2021</span>, <span style="color:#b452cd">6</span>, <span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>);
